<ul>
<li>“Our Jean-Jacques Rousseau”. <a href="/wiki/TELOS_(journal)" title="TELOS (journal)"><i>TELOS</i></a> 44 (Summer 1980). New York: <a href="http://www.telospress.com" class="external text" title="http://www.telospress.com" rel="nofollow">Telos Press</a></li>
