-noirs" title="Category:Pieds-noirs">Pieds-noirs</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Structuralism" title="Category:Structuralism">Structuralism</a></span></div><div id="mw-hidden-catlinks" class="mw-hidden-cats-hidden">Hidden categories:&#32;<span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Articles_needing_additional_references_from_September_2008" title="Category:Articles needing additional references from September 2008">Articles needing additional references from September 2008</a></span></div></div>			<!-- end content -->
